SIMPLE: inevitably
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Inevitably
<hw>In*ev"i*ta*bly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>Without possibility of
escape or evasion; unavoidably; certainly.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Inevitably</qex> thou shalt die.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>How <qex>inevitably</qex> does immoderate laughter end in a
sigh!</q> <rj><qau>South.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Inexact</ent>⟦br⟧
